Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.63,0:01:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戌时已到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉马上要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.24,0:01:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了找齐四魂之玉碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了用这把铁碎牙打败奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.17,0:01:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那么痛恨人类
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.35,0:01:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么身边\N偏偏带着人类的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸跟邪见\N再加上小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎会发生什么大事件呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师加上珊瑚\N七宝跟云母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿梭于时空\N发生在战国时代与现代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:44.15,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,分散在蓝蓝天空上的 七颗星星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.86,OP,,0,0,0,,每一颗星星 都刻着我的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.77,OP,,0,0,0,,就算梦想被粉碎 我也要寻找爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我无处可逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.87,OP,,0,0,0,,紧紧抓着我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:16.30,OP,,0,0,0,,那些骗人的光阴 我再也不会输给它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.37,0:02:21.67,OP,,0,0,0,,睁大眼睛 看清楚这瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:25.85,OP,,0,0,0,,它仍然紧紧围绕着我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:29.85,OP,,0,0,0,,让人啜泣的 现实生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.85,0:02:33.85,OP,,0,0,0,,最重要的…到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.72,OP,,0,0,0,,繁忙的这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:41.95,OP,,0,0,0,,永恒的碎片 忽隐又忽现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:45.87,OP,,0,0,0,,去触摸 去捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:52.80,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:58.03,OP,,0,0,0,,为了得到最后的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:05.27,OP,,0,0,0,,我们就要循着目标继续向前走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:20.59,*Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了寻找失踪的奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不断朝着\N丑寅方向前进的这个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.63,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉的哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也在寻找奈落的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第96话 邪见爷爷生病了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷\N小玲肚子快饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让小玲去找东西吃  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很烦耶  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想这座森林\N会有东西给你吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.23,0:04:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.00,0:04:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安静一点行不行…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下就回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信他竟然会…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直不敢相信耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把所有的东西都吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.85,0:04:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连最后一包\N大蒜味薯条也吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃你一两包薯条\N干嘛那么小气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我特地留下来\N想要拿去送给地念儿的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种口味你不是一向不吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道随便尝两口\N就会吃得停不下来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:38.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你说这下怎么办嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的地念儿是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.73,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  你们还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次云母\N不小心中了奈落的瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而治好它的消毒药\N就是地念儿给的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.34,0:04:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰巧这次\N会经过地念儿住的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想过去看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.22,0:04:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道\N送人的礼物居然被偷吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么偷吃嘛真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  这个地念儿也是个半妖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不过他很善良\N而且待人很好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和犬夜叉完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  既然送人的礼物吃光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆继续往前走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能拿到一些\N治疗瘴气的药
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了以后着想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看还是过去一趟比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上次云母的事\N我也想去谢谢人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  大家就一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至于犬夜叉\N你想怎样随你便咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.35,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙真是心胸狭窄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一定可以吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.34,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷果然厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷真的好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒虫最猛胜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不马上给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光会留下一些没用的废物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这附近\N应该有最猛胜的巢穴才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我马上去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个  毒虫的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔喔…嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.87,0:06:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一记  人头杖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些缠人的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  还不能把头抬起来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.55,0:07:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要保护小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道等等\N杀生丸少爷会怎么夸我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.26,0:07:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是得救啦  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果追过去看看的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  帮我拔出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拔出来没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:18.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘴气跟剧毒\N全都跑进我身体里面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子我死定了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:33.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.20,0:08:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道\N我可不是为了你才死的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了杀生丸少爷才死的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.07,0:08:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道\N有什么办法可以解毒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着解毒了  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟着杀生丸少爷这样到处游历
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.52,0:08:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直觉得自己好幸福喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:58.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这次就这么死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.36,0:09:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这一生也算死而无憾了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我转告杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就说我邪见会保佑他
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路上平安无事顺顺利利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得一定要转告他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样看着邪见爷爷死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什么都愿意帮你做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说些话嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就拜托你看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.03,0:09:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  你千万不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里一直向东走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.84,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会见到一个名叫\N“地念儿药草园”的药田
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.95,0:09:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到那去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我采一些“千年草的果实”回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“千年草的果实”?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的想救爷爷\N那就快去快回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.76,0:10:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果太阳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夕阳下山前  你还没有采到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“千年草的果实”回来救爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候\N最猛胜的剧毒会攻遍我全身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一定会没命了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧  邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会在\N太阳下山之前赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会赶回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.48,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是这里吗  戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…我想应该是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.59,0:10:42.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在这里没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉不是想怎样\N都随他便就可以了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.80,0:10:47.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点小事还在意那么久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起嘛  我刚刚说得太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙老是这样\N连道歉都那么没诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:10:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股味道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.68,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奈落那些毒虫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.99,0:11:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是一些\N专门扑火找死的夏虫嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.83,0:11:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别动手  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有感觉到\N四魂之玉碎片在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也感觉不到就在附近耶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没有感觉到那些奈落的傀儡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.84,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些毒虫说不定\N打算飞回奈落身边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别杀它们\N跟在后面看看再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说可以\N指引我们找到奈落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.23,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.43,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.37,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只最猛胜是你杀的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最猛胜?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是这只毒虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.45,0:12:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是思考肤浅的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻找奈落的线索一断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后要找他简直难如登天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先把话说在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这些毒虫自己突然死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么喜欢替自己狡辩\N你还是一样不要脸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁喜欢帮自己狡辩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.90,0:12:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过实话实说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛\N犬夜叉说的都是真话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  你给我让开一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟这小子多说无益
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我的心情不是很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要动起手来\N可不会像之前那样手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大话最好少说两句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N你才不要哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们两个\N别打了好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两兄弟还是一样感情不睦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽\N你在那边等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是药草园耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定不会错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请问一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是个山姥妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.34,0:13:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…我想见一下地念儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们家地念儿\N谁都不想见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地念儿在家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想来拜托他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想跟他要点千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个人中了剧毒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果找不到千年草果实救他\N他就要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可真是伤脑筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里\N已经没有千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.86,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.50,0:14:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么躲在被子里不出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出来不怕你见笑\N其实是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的地念儿是个半妖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半妖?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有时候会像现在这样\N变成一个普通人类
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏这孩子胆子又特别小
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他变成人类的时候\N根本不想让人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不可以告诉我\N哪里可以采到千年草的果实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己可以去采
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实\N是用来解妖怪剧毒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成…你是想要救妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会是\N看上那个妖怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.17,0:14:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是看上妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  原来你还不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事慢慢你一定会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:59.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得当年我也跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婆婆先别提这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很希望能救邪见爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉不觉得这个小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戈薇姑娘很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.00,0:15:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的是那个姑娘呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许是有那么点像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.44,0:15:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实\N就长在后山的山谷里头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.14,0:15:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里住着魑魅魍魉各种妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人类其实很难采得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等天黑之后\N我就可以恢复正常
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等一等\N天黑之后我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我那些草长什么样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己爬上去采
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟戈薇姑娘还真像耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲  杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:16:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想…一个人\N孤零零的死去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你的  去死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:17.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胜负已定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.68,0:16:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我觉悟吧  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呸  我才不像你那么怕死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.59,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干嘛随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.59,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.52,0:16:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也想要知道\N奈落的行踪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈落就在丑寅方向
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说奈落最后的形迹\N是往那边移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这条线索就容易多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这条命暂时寄放一下\N犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别走  杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛要追奈落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.48,0:17:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放过他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  阿吽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.85,0:17:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.29,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于找到了  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿吽  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先帮我守着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去采千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸  妈妈  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的人都死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的\N不希望再有其他人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的\N不希望看见其他人死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.61,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  不要死…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.11,0:19:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望再有人死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毒性开始发作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  太阳就快下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小玲是赶不及回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始觉得眼花了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.13,0:20:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀…杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.22,0:21:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪见爷爷  你不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦?你说有个小姑娘\N来找过地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.87,0:21:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  不晓得她是不是\N能平安的采到千年草的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真替她担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒觉得她一定没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小姑娘\N跟戈薇姑娘很像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说她跟戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.38,0:21:35.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信那位小姑娘\N一定比我强得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:41.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就像戈薇姑娘一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一颗温暖的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.95,0:21:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像太阳一样的小姑娘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信等她长大之后\N一定也有一颗善良的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地念儿  你别再说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.76,0:21:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你恐怕对戈薇有些误解吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.97,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.47,0:22:01.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇这个人\N很令人意外的小心眼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.41,0:22:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.75,0:22:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见了吧  地念儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说她心胸狭窄嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下  给我坐下…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.52,0:22:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.57,0:22:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  你终于醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:35.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  邪见爷爷\N你已经好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.97,0:22:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说\N连我…都一起死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.95,0:22:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷救了你\N还把你带回来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.38,0:22:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错啊  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不能再麻烦\N杀生丸少爷咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.16,0:22:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.76,0:22:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过邪见爷爷  还好你好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.66,0:23:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哭什么啊  小玲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点放开我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.73,0:23:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.53,0:23:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丑寅方向是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:07.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生丸少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.32,0:23:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很高兴\N大家又可以在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:56.65,ED,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.50,0:23:34.15,ED,,0,0,0,,红红的太阳照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:43.95,ED,,0,0,0,,也照遍过去和现在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.10,0:23:53.22,ED,,0,0,0,,那些夕阳下的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.52,0:24:03.22,ED,,0,0,0,,这颗心真的能承担吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:08.20,ED,,0,0,0,,告诉我什么办法才能
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:13.12,ED,,0,0,0,,活得比以前更开朗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.12,0:24:20.52,ED,,0,0,0,,这么做就算会让自己委屈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.40,0:24:27.07,ED,,0,0,0,,要默默承受伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.07,0:24:31.25,ED,,0,0,0,,会失去一切
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.65,0:24:38.50,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌仍会不断在我心中回荡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.95,0:24:48.52,ED,,0,0,0,,真正的歌才是我的路标
